==Awards==
*[[Academy Award]]
**1974: Nominated, [[Academy Award for Writing Adapted Screenplay|Best Adapted Screenplay]], ''[[The Last Detail]]''
**1975: Won, [[Academy Award for Writing Original Screenplay|Best Original Screenplay]], ''Chinatown''
**1976: Nominated, Best Original Screenplay, ''Shampoo''
**1985:  Nominated, Best Adapted Screenplay, ''Greystoke: The Legend of Tarzan''
*[[British Academy of Film and Television Arts|BAFTA Award]]
**1975: Won, Best Screenplay, ''The Last Detail'' and ''Chinatown''
*[[Golden Globe Award]]
**1975: Won, Best Screenplay - Motion Picture, ''Chinatown''
*[[Edgar Award]]

